	-on activities with a giant free-build area\, LEGO displays and models\, s
	hopping and photo ops. The event is free to attend. Attendees will be admi
	tted as space allows.  Do you have a LEGO build worth sharing? We're now a
	ccepting exhibitor applications. Apply here: https://issaquahhighlands.com
	/?p=65836 Thanks to our sponsors for making this event possible: Highlands
	 Fiber Network\, Issaquah Ice Cream Trike and Bricks and Minifigs.\n\nhttp
	s://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/issaquah-highlands-lego-expo/182
